                                <td class="px-4 py-4"><code class="font-mono font-medium text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400">Type</code></td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400"><code>AccordionType</code> enum – Determines how accordion sections behave when opened.
                                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                                        <li><code class="rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">AccordionType.Multiple</code>: Allows multiple sections to be expanded simultaneously.</li>
                                        <li><code class="rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">AccordionType.Single</code>: Ensures only one section is open at a time; opening a new section closes any previously open one.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-4"><code class="font-mono text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400">AccordionType</code></td>
